# Client privacy rules.
#
# These are NOT active in the starter repo (so it can track clients/_template
# and clients/README.md). The `intake` agent appends this block to .gitignore on
# first run, so once you onboard a real client their brief + downloaded assets
# (which contain PII and large binaries) are never committed.
#
# To apply manually:  cat .gitignore.template >> .gitignore

# --- client privacy ---
/clients/*
!/clients/_template/
!/clients/README.md
